The morpho-functional changes of the follicular apparatus and yellow body of the ovary in women of the reproductive age with myoma. It have been studied the morpho-functional changes of the ovaries in women of reproductive age with proliferative myoma of uteri. Based on the analysis of the result of the investigation on the myomatic knots of the women in the condition of high activity of proliferation of myocytes a very complexes, multifactorial pathogenetic mechanisms of the myoma has been outlined. Switch in the common changes in the dynamic oxidative stress and hyperestrogenemia promotes development of the myoma.